Name:		kmahjongg
Summary:	A tile laying patience
Version:	4.14.3
Release:	1
Epoch:		1
Group:		Graphical desktop/KDE
License:	GPLv2 and LGPLv2 and GFDL
URL:		http://games.kde.org/game.php?game=kmahjongg
